  • Klassen
    Klasse
    Beschreibung
    ApiService
    Service for fetching movie and series information via the OMDb API (In Our Context there is a difference between anime and series but OMDb does not make this difference).
    CineFactoryService
    Factory service for creating Cinematic objects by combining CSV data with API information.
    CsvImporterService
    Service for importing and parsing CSV files containing cinematic data.
    CsvParserService
    Service for parsing and validating CSV data types, states, and ratings.
    DialogService
    Service for creating and displaying JavaFX dialog alerts.
    LineValidatorService
    Service for validating CSV file headers and records.
    LogService
    Singleton service for logging application events with different severity levels.
    SessionManagerService
    Singleton service managing user session state.
    ViewLoaderService
    Service for loading and managing JavaFX views and scenes.
